{
  "stem": "182.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "The old people, they will take care of the children, or cooking, and washing, and the young people will work.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And my mother always said, I wouldn't like to do that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I would like to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "My father, he was very worried that they were going to take the young women to the soldiers to the front.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And he had enough, be-- before we went to the s-- to the synagogue, he stopped in the pharmacy and he got poison that if he w-- and he had a syringe.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "That he had an idea that we should kill ourselves.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "That we shouldn't go through this, because nothing is, you know, and they're gonna-- we should kill ourselves.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And when he told us, I told Daddy-- and I don't know where I took the courage, because my-- my mother and father, they're very, very strict people-- and I told my-- my father, Daddy, I'm so young.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I never even loved, or was loved by somebody.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I don't want to die.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And don't worry, if they taking-- they will take us to the-- for something like that, there's always a way that I can kill myself.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And so he didn't do it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And then the train finally, after three days, stopped.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Then they opened the doors and there were the Germans with the German shepherds and-- dogs-- and there were some inmates in striped uniforms.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they told us that, first of all, to separate men from women, and line up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was Mengele.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is a man-- very handsome, dark man-- with a big, black cape, with a-- with a crop.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "With a crop.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "With black boots, shiny boots.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
